## Performance & Standards

- **Zero Build Tools**: No webpack/vite/npm required for the frontend.
- **Native Shadow DOM**: Styles are encapsulated within each component.
- **Constructable Stylesheets**: Shared primitives (buttons, inputs) are distributed efficiently.
